	* gtkttyos.c: #ifdef stuff for HAVE_SYS_WAIT_H and HAVE_GETRLIMIT,
	added defualt value for closing of all file descriptors.  

	* main.c: (gvt_signal_handler): return type is of RETSIGTYPE now.

